    "description": {
      "value": "<p><strong>Scroll of Stoneskin</strong> (Level 4 Abjuration)</p><p>This spell turns the flesh of a willing creature you touch as hard as stone. Until the spell ends, the target has resistance to nonmagical bludgeoning, piercing, and slashing damage.</p><p><strong>Components:</strong> V, S, M (Diamond dust worth 100 gp, which the spell consumes.)</p><p><strong>Casting Time:</strong> 1 action | <strong>Range:</strong> Touch | <strong>Duration:</strong> Up to 1 hour (Concentration)</p><p><em>Classes: Druid, Ranger, Sorcerer, Wizard</em></p>",
